# mdBook build output and assembled-at-build-time source tree.
# Canonical sources live at VISION.md, SPEC.md, and ADR/*.md;
# .github/workflows/docs.yml copies them into docs-book/ at build time.
# Only docs-book/SUMMARY.md and docs-book/README.md (the nav tree + landing
# page) are tracked — everything else under docs-book/ is a build-time copy
# and must stay out of git.
book/
docs-book/VISION.md
docs-book/SPEC.md
docs-book/ADR/
